23
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:48,039
Don't do such brainless things again

24
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,560
As for that physician who knows

25
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,080
get rid of her

26
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,460
You want me to kill Chunyu Yan?

27
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,760
You know too much

28
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,760
Go join your master

29
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,240
You!

30
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:13,760
