31
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,480
What a vicious heart!

32
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,120
Don't worry

33
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,530
That little junior sister of yours

34
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:21,760
