35
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:27,880
Yan Fei.

36
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:28,640
What are you doing?

37
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:29,200
Stop!

38
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:34,930
Miss Chunyu.

39
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,240
Miss Chunyu.

40
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,290
Miss Chunyu.

41
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,450
Miss Chunyu.

42
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,380
I never thought

43
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:49,200
I would end up lying in your arms like this.

44
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,079
I know

45
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:57,040
that I've never truly been in your heart.

46
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,560
But it's alright.

47
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:00,720
I just

48
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,960
feared that

49
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,440
I would never see you again.

50
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,010
Miss Chunyu.

51
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,480
Help!

52
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,480
Miss,

53
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,890
are you alright?

54
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,280
Do you know?

55
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:43,040
Do you know how painful it is to give your heart to the wrong person?

56
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,570
Miss Chunyu,

57
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,840
I went too far last time,

58
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,680
I'm sorry.

59
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,800
What happened to her?

60
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,240
Yan Xier did this.

61
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,820
Go quickly and apply medicine to her wounds.

62
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,320
The

63
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:13,720
formula for the life-saving pills.

64
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,240
I found two ingredients

65
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,120
that I've tested

66
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,089
and can be used as medicine.

67
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:24,800
I never intended to take the medical book,

68
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,920
I just wanted to look at it.

69
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,640
I never thought

70
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:33,440
this would anger Master to death.

71
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,080
Miss Chunyu.

72
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:38,680
Senior Sister.

73
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:41,200
Senior Sister, I know you'll be fine, Senior Sister.

74
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,260
I know everything.

75
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:46,520
You finally called me Senior Sister again.

76
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:52,000
Take good care of yourself from now on.

77
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,520
And also...

78
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,760
Senior Sister!

79
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,760
Miss Chunyu, Senior Sister.

80
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,000
Miss Chunyu.

81
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,860
Senior Sister.

82
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,440
Miss Chunyu.

83
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,300
Senior Sister.

84
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,860
Senior Sister.

85
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:25,020
Thank you for taking care of me all these years, Senior Sister.

86
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,020
Senior Sister.

87
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,240
Senior Sister.

88
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,400
Senior Sister.

