Senior Sister.

90
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,480
Senior Sister.

91
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,320
Learn to please the Emperor,

92
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,800
keep him wrapped around your finger,

93
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,060
and use him for our Huo family's benefit.

94
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,680
What are you going to do?

95
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,560
What did you do to my senior sister?

96
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,820
I'll do the same to you.

97
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:09,920
Sister.

98
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,080
For our father's sake,

99
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,560
please don't kill me.

100
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:17,200
When father was alive, you took my place by his side,

101
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,000
fulfilling my filial duties.

102
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:22,000
But I must avenge my senior sister.

103
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,770
I'm giving you these scissors.

104
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,760
Remember that you've used them to kill.

105
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,580
If you ever do it again,

106
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:32,010
I will show no mercy.

107
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,800
You finally called me Senior Sister again.

108
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,000
That's enough for me.

109
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:56,400
Little Junior Sister, I'm going to join our master now.

110
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:58,840
From now on, you'll be alone in the palace.

111
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,890
Take good care of yourself.

112
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,260
Senior Sister.

113
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,280
I'm sorry.

114
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,610
I couldn't bring myself to harm Yan Xi'er.

115
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,400
I hope you can forgive me.

116
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,000
You're hurt.

117
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:34,000
With Yan Jie Huan's temperament,

118
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,400
if Huo Fang kills her now,

119
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:38,890
she will certainly reveal everything about Chun Yu Yan.

120
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,450
It was just an accident.

121
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:45,720
I heard the Emperor hasn't eaten your desserts for days.

122
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,090
I suppose he's probably tired of them.

123
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:50,960
Find a way

124
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,200
to make him eat this.

125
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,659
When the time is right,

126
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:58,600
I will take you back to our mansion and restore your Huo family name.

127
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,160
Mother loved you her entire life,

128
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,490
yet you watched her die,

129
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,220
and you've only been using me.

130
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,680
If you want to be my father again,

131
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,560
it depends on whether I allow it.

132
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,140
You've been waiting here.

133
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,210
I don't know how to comfort you,

134
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,530
so I thought I'd just keep you company.

135
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:33,799
But now I don't have any family left.

136
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,919
But you still have me.

137
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,120
The Lantern Festival is coming up in a few days,

138
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:49,050
I'll take you there to cheer you up.

139
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,320
Good medicine tastes bitter,

140
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,640
bitter first, then sweet.

141
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:06,240
If you don't believe me, Your Highness, try it.

142
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,340
It's too bitter. I won't drink it.

143
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,370
How about trying again?

144
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,520
Come,

145
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,760
take another sip.

146
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,840
Come, take another sip.

147
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,480
Your Majesty,

148
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,560
Eunuch Li has urgent matters to report to you.

149
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,400
Why so flustered?

150
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:50,280
What happened?

151
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:53,690
Your Majesty, the miscarriage was not caused by Doctor Yan.

152
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:56,040
Someone ordered me to frame him.

153
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,180
But Doctor Yan once saved my life,

154
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:01,240
and I cannot stand by

155
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:03,280
while he suffers this injustice.

156
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,120
Quickly, who was it?

157
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,120
That person is...

158
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,200
is...

159
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,280
Sister, come catch me!

160
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,300
Shi'er, slow down.

161
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,580
From what I can see,

162
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,280
she was truly wronged.

163
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,780
She was genuinely caring toward Shi'er.

164
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,680
Shi'er's health has improved,

165
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:35,920
he doesn't need to take medicine anymore.

166
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:38,240
When you have time, take him out more often

167
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,640
to build up his strength.

168
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:42,440
I've heard about Physician Chunyu's situation.

169
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,280
The one-month deadline has arrived,

170
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,680
yet she has encountered such misfortune.

171
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,680
It's truly a pity.

172
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:47,920
From now on,

173
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:50,650
you shall remain at the Imperial Medical Bureau.

174
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,410
I obey your command.

175
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,280
Shi'er has been raised in the inner palace,

176
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:56,010
and I cannot easily go outside.

177
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,120
I hear you and the Prince are going to the Lantern Festival.

178
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,720
Why not take Shi'er with you?

179
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:00,920
I want to see

180
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:02,300
the lantern festival.

181
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,000
Alright.

182
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:04,170
Sister will take you

183
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,120
there.

184
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,400
I am the Empress.

185
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,380
The one I should really care about is Shi'er,

186
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,960
he is my only support.

